{"tid":898934,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"《愛的種子》首歌係講乜？","createTime":"2018-11-12T04:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T05:24:59.000Z","uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"da9737a5a397e56fcfa7a230b1e49faf219fd7c1","tid":898934,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T04:57:22.000Z","msg":"上星期第一次聽到呢首歌，覺得好正，想問下首歌係想講乜野story<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：IQ = 50，番緊庇護工場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n愛的種子<br />\n<br />\n作詞：鄭國江<br />\n作曲：林子祥<br />\n<br />\n為何面上滿是遲疑<br />\n何事妳眼中含淚<br />\n情和義原是相對<br />\n一段情等待妳<br />\n<br />\n妳的心若早經相許<br />\n何事妳卻想迴避<br />\n情和義是容易失去<br />\n心上愁卻揮不去<br />\n<br />\n妳可知　她的心<br />\n她的心　像小種子<br />\n埋在妳那冰一般心裡<br />\n自然會恨透妳<br />\n<br />\n愛好比　小種子<br />\n它的根　在心中開始<br />\n明白妳每當夜半夢乍醒<br />\n不禁一聲聲嘆氣"},{"pid":"63ab112d30079997cf35e6319d3a9b49dc48bf77","tid":898934,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T10:18:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b431423168a8c95d937980b4f19b5ef5889f4094","tid":898934,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T14:51:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd0a5a0e31ccbf0c8599a3e16d9f1ef7c21bffa0","tid":898934,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T05:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}